subtests.name: Property text-decoration value 'none' computes to 'none solid rgb(0, 0, 255)'
Property text-decoration value 'line-through' computes to 'line-through solid rgb(0, 0, 255)'
Property text-decoration value 'solid' computes to 'none solid rgb(0, 0, 255)'
Property text-decoration value 'currentcolor' computes to 'none solid rgb(0, 0, 255)'
Property text-decoration value 'double overline underline' computes to 'underline overline double rgb(0, 0, 255)'
Property text-decoration value 'underline overline line-through red' computes to 'underline overline line-through solid rgb(255, 0, 0)'
Property text-decoration value 'rgba(10, 20, 30, 0.4) dotted' computes to 'none dotted rgba(10, 20, 30, 0.4)'
Property text-decoration value 'underline dashed rgb(0, 255, 0)' computes to 'underline dashed rgb(0, 255, 0)'
